Detailed Description

cvmx_prch_ant_num0

This register reports which input antennae are mapped to PRCH antennae 0-7.

The i^th antenna in the j^th sector configured in PRCH maps is antenna (N*j + i), where N is either 2, 4, or 8, depending on whether PRCH is in 2 antenna, 4 antenna, or 8 antenna mode.
